REFERENCE           SABER_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Lightsaber\nAn elegant weapon for a more civilized age, the lightsaber is the preferred weapon of the Jedi Knight.  The lightsaber is an energy blade of great power that can be used by the wielder for both attack and defense.\nPrimary Fire - Slashing and swinging attacks\nSecondary Fire - Force powered saber throw\nDefensive Ability - Deflects blaster and energy weapon fire, parries enemy lightsaber attacks\nAmmo Type - N/A"
LANG_CZECH        "Svetelny mec\nSvetelny mec je elegantni zbrani pro civilizovanejsi vek a je uprednostnovan rytiri Jedi. Svetelny mec je energetickou cepeli velke sily, ktera muze byt pouzita svym drzitelem jak k utoku, tak k obrane.\n\nPrimarni utok - Sekani a svihani\nSekundarni utok - Hod mecem za pomoci Sily\nObranna schopnost - Odrazi strelbu z blasteru a dalsich energetickych zbrani, odvraci utoky nepratelskeho svetelneho mece\nDruh naboju - Zadne"

REFERENCE           NEW_BLASTER_PISTOL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DL-44 Heavy Blaster Pistol \nOne of the most common firearms in the galaxy, the DL-44 Heavy Blaster Pistol is a hand-held energy weapon with a slow rate of fire and incredible accuracy.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with great accuracy and damage\nSecondary Fire - Charged energy buildup for increased damage blast attack\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Tezka blasterova pistole DL-44\nTezka blasterova pistole DL-44 je jednou z nejbeznejsich zbrani v galaxii. Ma nizkou kadenci, ale je vysoce presna.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a silou\nSekundarni utok - Vytrysk nahromadene nabite energie s vyssi silou\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           ALONGTIME
LANG_ENGLISH        "A long time ago in a galaxy far,\nfar away...."
LANG_CZECH        "Pred davnymi casy v galaxii lezici\ndaleko, daleko odsud..."

REFERENCE           BLASTER_PISTOL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Bryar Blaster Pistol \nKyle Katarn's weapon of choice, the Bryar Blaster Pistol is a common hand-held energy weapon with a slow rate of fire and incredible accuracy.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with great accuracy and damage\nSecondary Fire - Charged energy buildup for increased damage blast attack\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Blasterova pistole Bryar\nBlasterova pistole Bryar je oblibenou zbrani Kyle Katarna a beznou rucni energetickou zbrani s nizkou kadenci a neuveritelnou presnosti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a silou\nSekundardni utok - Vytrysk nahromadene nabite energie s vyssi silou\Druh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           BLASTER_RIFLE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "E-11 Blaster Rifle \nThe primary weapon of the Imperial forces, the E-11 is a sturdy and deadly blaster rifle capable of inflicting great damage despite its small size.  The E-11's compact design makes it easy to carry and conceal.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with moderate accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid, burst fire with low accuracy and expanded firing area\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Blasterova puska E-11\nE-11 je zakladni zbrani vojaku Imperia. Je to stabilni a smrtici blasterova puska schopna zpusobit velke skody navzdory sve male velikosti.  Kompaktni design E-11 umoznuje jeji snadne noseni a ukryti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel se stredni presnosti a velkou silou\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a vyssim palebnym dosahem\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           DISRUPTOR_RIFLE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tenloss DXR-6 Disruptor rifle \nThis nefarious weapon affects matter at the molecular level, ripping apart living material with ease.   Because of the weapon's inhumane nature, the DXR-6 is outlawed throughout the galaxy and is generally only used by scattered droid and Remnant forces.\nPrimary Fire - Single shot with slow fire rate, fast projectile and small radius damage\nSecondary Fire - Scoped mode: Single shot with slow fire rate, increased damage and high weapon energy consumption\nAmmo Type - Power cell"
LANG_CZECH        "Tenlosska disruptorova puska DXR-6\nTato ohavna zbran ovlivnuje hmotu na molekularni urovni a snadno trha na kusy zivy material. Vzhledem k nelidske povaze zbrane je DXR-6 zakazana v cele galaxii a obecne ji pouzivaji pouze roztrousene jednotky droidu a zbylych vojaku Imperia.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden vystrel s nizkou kadenci, rychlou strelou a malym okruhem poskozeni\nSekundarni utok - Odstrelovaci mod: Jeden vystrel s nizkou kadenci, vyssim poskozenim a vysokou energetickou spotrebou\nDruh naboju - Energeticky clanek"

REFERENCE           BOWCASTER_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Wookiee Bowcaster\nThis archaic-looking weapon fires powerful bolts of metal enveloped in pockets of energy.  Capable of inflicting incredible damage, the bowcaster requires tremendous physical strength to fire.  Most bowcasters sold outside the Wookiee homeworld come equipped with self-cocking actions that allow physically weaker creatures to fire them.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with radius damage.  Hold FIRE to charge weapon for spread attack\nSecondary Fire - Unleashes a reflective shot that bounces off solid surfaces\nAmmo Type - Power cell"
LANG_CZECH        "Wookijska kuse\nTato zastarale vyhlizejici zbran pali silne kovove strely zabalene do energetickych obalu, je schopna zpusobit neuveritelne skody a ke strelbe z ni je treba ohromne fyzicke sily. Vetsina kusi prodanych mimo wookijskou domovinu je vybavena samonatahovacim mechanismem, aby z nich mohly strilet i fyzicky slabsi bytosti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s kruhovym poskozenim. Abyste nabili zbran k sirsimu utoku, podrzte STRELBU\nSekundardni utok - Vypali strelu, ktera se odrazi od pevnych povrchu\nDruh naboju - Energeticky clanek"

REFERENCE           HEAVYREPEATER_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Imperial Heavy Repeater with Concussion Launcher\nThis destructive projectile weapon is extremely deadly, firing rapid streams of metal bullets.  Imperial forces use the Heavy Repeater's deadly suppressive fire and concussion launcher for crowd control and to spread heavy fire over large areas.\nPrimary Fire - Fully automatic projectile fire \nSecondary Fire - Single shot, concussion explosive round\nAmmo type - Metallic bolts"
LANG_CZECH        "Tezky imperialni opakovac s odpalovacem narazovych granatu\nTato niciva strelna zbran je vysoce smrtici a pali rychle davky kovovych kulek. Vojaci Imperia pouzivaji smrtici strelbu tezkeho opakovace a jeho odpalovac narazovych granatu k ovladnuti davu a k rozptyleni tezke palby po velkych oblastech.\n\nPrimarni utok - Plne automaticka projektilova palba\nSekundarni utok - Jedna explozivni strela s narazovym granatem\nDruh naboju - Kovove kulky"

REFERENCE           DEMP2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Destructive Electro-Magnetic Pulse 2 Gun\nCommonly referred to as the DEMP 2, this pulse rifle is primarily used against droids and electrical devices.  The DEMP 2 fires high-powered ion bursts that disrupt electrical systems.  Unlike previous incarnations of the weapon, the DEMP 2's ion charges are capable of damaging living material.\nPrimary Fire - Single shot, stuns humans, damages droids\nSecondary Fire - Charged energy attack that creates an expanding shell of electromagnetic energy on impact that damages humanoids, droids and turrets\nAmmo Type - Power cell"
LANG_CZECH        "Niciva elektromagneticka pulsni puska typu 2\nTato puska se bezne nazyva DEMP 2 a pouziva se predevsim proti droidum\na elektrickym zarizenim. DEMP 2 strili vysokoenergeticke iontove paprsky, ktere narusuji elektricke systemy. Oproti predchozim verzim teto zbrane jsou iontove naboje DEMP2 schopne poranit zivy material.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden vystrel, ktery omraci lidi a poskodi droidy\nSekundarni utok - Nabita strela, ktera pri dopadu vytvori zvetsujici se vlnu elektromagneticke energie, ktera porani humanoidy a ponici droidy a veze\nDruh naboju - Energeticky clanek"

REFERENCE           FLECHETTE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Golan Arms FC1 Flechette Weapon \nWidely used by the Corporate Sector Authority's police squads, the FC1 fires shards of red-hot metal in a widespread pattern.   The weapon is designed to hit multiple targets in close proximity, but great care must be taken to avoid ricochet damage.\nPrimary Fire - Single shot, spread fire\nSecondary Fire - Fires two bouncing shield-protected proximity mines which explode after a short time\nAmmo Type - Metallic Bolts"
LANG_CZECH        "Golanska rucni flechettova zbran FC1\nFC1 je siroce pouzivana policejnimi jednotkami uradu firemniho sektoru a strili kovove strepiny v rozprostrenem vzorci. Zbran je navrzena tak, aby zasahla nekolik cilu na malou vzdalenost, ale drzitel si musi davat pozor, aby se vyhnul nebezpeci odrazenych strel.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden rozprostreny vystrel\nSekundardni utok - Vypali dve odrazejici se miny reagujici na blizkost, ktere vybuchnou po kratke chvili\nDruh naboju - Kovove kulky"

REFERENCE           CONCUSSION_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Stouker Concussion Rifle  \nThe Stouker fires a concussive blast creating an implosion that spreads about 4 meters in diameter.\nPrimary Fire - Single shot, large implosive effect that damages everything, slow firing rate\nSecondary Fire - Fires a smaller projectile shot that has a smaller explosive radius but does much more damage in that radius and has a more severe recoil\nAmmo Type - Metallic Bolts"
LANG_CZECH        "Narazova puska Stouker\nStouker strili narazovy vyboj, ktery vytvori explozi, ktera se rozsiri priblizne do ctyr metru v prumeru.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jedna rana, velky vybusny ucinek, ktery poskodi vsechno, nizka kadence\nSekundarni utok - Strili mensi projektil, ktery ma mensi polomer vybuchu, ale v tomto okruhu nadela vice skod a ma silnejsi zpetny raz\nDruh naboju - Kovove kulky"

REFERENCE           MERR_SONN_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Merr-Sonn PLX-2M Portable Missile System   \nThe PLX-2M is an extremely powerful weapon that fires Arakyd 3T3 missiles.  The sheer explosive power of the PLX-2M makes it dangerous to fire blindly in close quarters, but is extremely effective when used as a 'smart' tracking weapon.\nPrimary Fire - Fires a single, forward-firing explosive missile\nSecondary Fire - Fires a single 'smart' missile that tracks acquired and locked targets\nAmmo Type - Rockets"
LANG_CZECH        "Prenosny raketovy system Merr-Sonn PLX-2M\nPLX-2M je extremne silnou zbrani, ktera strili rakety Arakyd 3T3. Pouha explozivni sila PLX-2M cini tuto zbran nebezpecnou pro strelbu naslepo v tesnych prostorach, ale je velice ucinna pouzije-li se jako 'chytra' navadeci zbran.\n\nPrimarni utok - Strili jednu explozivni raketu letici rovne kupredu \nSekundarni utok - Strili jednu 'chytrou' raketu, ktera sleduje zamerene cile\nDruh naboju - Rakety"

REFERENCE           THERMAL_DETONATOR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Thermal Detonator \nThe thermal detonator is a radius-damage grenade that releases a barrage of thermal energy capable of disintegrating all matter around it.\nPrimary Fire - Detonator explodes after a short time.  Press FIRE longer for longer throw\nSecondary Fire - Detonator explodes on impact.  Press ALT-FIRE longer for longer throw"
LANG_CZECH        "Termalni detonator\nTermalni detonator je granatem, ktery v urcitem okruhu kolem sebe uvolni vlnu termalni energie, ktera je schopna rozlozit veskerou hmotu.\n\nPrimarni utok - Granat exploduje po kratkem case. Pro delsi hod podrzte dele STRELBU\nSekundarni utok - Granat exploduje pri kontaktu. Pro delsi hod podrzte dele ALTERNATIVNI STRELBU"

REFERENCE           TRIP_MINE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Trip Mines \nTrip mines consist of a beam projector affixed to a shaped explosive casing.  The laser activates when the mine is placed and extends a beam from the charge to the nearest surface that intersects its path.  If the beam is broken or the charge is fired upon, the mine detonates and causes radius damage to anything in range.\nPrimary Fire - Once placed, triggered by breaking the beam\nSecondary Fire - Once placed, the mine acts as a proximity device, waiting until an enemy comes within blast radius, then detonates, damaging any enemies in the area"
LANG_CZECH        "Nastrazne miny\nNastrazne miny se skladaji z projektoru paprsku pripevneneho k vytvarovanemu vybusnemu obalu.  Laser se aktivuje pri polozeni miny a paprsek saha od naloze\nk nejblizsi prekazce, ktera krizuje jeho cestu. Je-li paprsek prerusen nebo nekdo na minu vystreli, mina detonuje a zpusobi skody na vsem v urcitem okruhu kolem sebe.\n\nPrimarni utok - Po polozeni vybuchne, je-li paprsek prerusen\nSekundarni utok - Po polozeni se mina chova jako zarizeni na zjistovani blizkeho pohybu a ceka, dokud nepritel neprijde do oblasti vybuchu. Pote vybuchne a porani vsechny nepratele v oblasti"

REFERENCE           DET_PACK_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Detonation Packs \nA detonation pack is essentially a small explosive device with a remote detonation trigger.  The pack is placed or thrown and can be detonated at will by the user.  Detonation packs are commonly used to ambush enemies or open sealed doors.\nPrimary Fire - Sets charge at the user's feet\nSecondary Fire - Explodes all set charges"
LANG_CZECH        "Vybusne naloze\nVybusna naloz je v podstate male explozivni zarizeni s dalkovym ovladanim. Majitel naloze ji muze polozit nebo hodit a pote ji odpalit podle vlastniho uvazeni. Vybusne naloze se bezne pouzivaji k vytvareni lecky na nepratele nebo k otevreni zamcenych dveri.\n\nPrimarni utok - Hodi naloz k noham majitele\nSekundarni utok - Vyhodi do vzduchu vsechny polozene naloze"

REFERENCE           STUN_BATON_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Stun Baton \nCommonly used to subdue unruly prisoners, the stun baton was designed for use in melee combat where killing your opponent is not necessarily the desired outcome.\nPrimary Fire - Short range jabbing electrical stun attack\nSecondary Fire - None"
LANG_CZECH        "Obusek na omraceni\nObusek na omraceni se bezne pouziva k podrobeni vzpurnych veznu a byl navrzen pro pouziti v sarvatkach, kde zabiti Vaseho protivnika nutne neni pozadovanym vysledkem.\n\nPrimarni utok - Omracujici bodavy elektricky vyboj na kratkou vzdalenost\nSekundarni utok - Zadne"

REFERENCE           NEURO_SAAV_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Neuro-Saav Model TD2.3 Electrobinoculars\nElectrobinoculars operate in low-light and normal light conditions to magnify distant objects and provide a heads-up display that features detailed information on the area viewed.  The heads-up display measures distances and offers various telemetry readouts on the object or area in view. Powered by normal battery cells that drain power at a minimal rate."
LANG_CZECH        "Elektrodalekohled Neuro-Saav model TD2.3\nElektrodalekohled funguje v prostredi s nizkym o normalnim osvetlenim, zvetsuje vzdalene objekty a obsahuje informacni displej, ktery obsahuje detailni informace o pozorovane oblasti. Informacni displej meri vzdalenost a nabizi ruzne telemetricke udaje o pozorovanem objektu nebo oblasti. Je napajen normalnimi bateriemi, ze kterych cerpa energii v minimalni mire."

REFERENCE           BACTA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BioTech Bacta Canister\nBacta canisters are portable, disposable packs of bacta ointments and emergency care tools.  Designed for use in the field, bacta canisters can be used to heal wounds and restore vitality during medical recovery.  No field medic should be without them."
LANG_CZECH        "Kanistry biotechnicke bacty\nKanistry bacty jsou prenosna, jednorazova baleni masti bacta a nouzovych pecovatelskych nastroju. Kanistry bacty jsou navrzeny pro pouziti v poli a lze je pouzit k leceni zraneni a obnove zivotni sily behem zotaveni. Zadny polni medik by bez nich nemel byt."

REFERENCE           INQUISITOR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Seeker Drone\nAn attack drone similar to the training drones used by Jedi to practice their lightsaber skills, the Seeker hovers around its user and attacks any enemy the user fires upon.  The drone operates automatically for a limited time and then self-destructs\nwhen its power is depleted."
LANG_CZECH        "Utocny droid\nUtocny droid je podobny vycvikovym droidum, ktere pouzivaji Jediove k procviceni svych dovednosti se svetelnym mecem. Vznasi se kolem sveho majitele a utoci na nepritele, na ktereho majitel strili. Droid funguje automaticky po omezenou dobu a pote se sam znici, kdyz se vycerpa jeho energie."

REFERENCE           LA_GOGGLES_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Light Amplification Goggles\nAlso known as infra-goggles, this helpful device creates a balance of light levels that allows the user to see well in most situations. The resulting effect enhances the overall brightness but casts everything in a greenish hue. The goggles require batteries to function, draining them at roughly the same rate as Electrobinoculars.   Light Amplification Goggles can be worn during combat, but will not function without an available power source."
LANG_CZECH        "Bryle zesilujici svetlo\nToto uzitecne zarizeni, zname rovnez jako infra-bryle, vykalibrovava urovne svetla, cimz umoznuje svemu majiteli videt dobre ve vetsine situaci. Vysledny efekt zvysuje celkovy jas, ale zobrazuje vse v nazelenalem odstinu. Ke svemu fungovani vyzaduji bryle baterie, ktere vycerpavaji zhruba stejnou rychlosti jako elektrodalekohled. Bryle zesilujici svetlo lze pouzit v bitve, ale nebudou fungovat bez dostupneho energetickeho zdroje."

REFERENCE           PORTABLE_SENTRY_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Portable Assault Sentry  \nThis deadly weapon is roughly the size of a large backpack, but don't let its size fool you. Once activated, the weapon unfurls and is set to auto-target any enemy threat. The Sentry drains battery life at an accelerated rate and, once it's deployed, can't be restored to its original portable condition."
LANG_CZECH        "Prenosna utocna hlidkova vez\nTato smrtici zbran je zhruba velikosti velkeho batohu, ale tim se nenechte oklamat. Po aktivaci se tato zbran roztahne a nastavi se na automaticke zamerovani jakekoliv nepratelske hrozby. Vez cerpa energii z baterie zvysenou rychlosti a je-li baterie vycerpana, nelze vez obnovit do jejiho puvodniho prenosneho stavu."

REFERENCE           SECURITY_KEY_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Security Key"
LANG_CZECH        "Bezpecnosti klic"

REFERENCE           EMPTY_INV
LANG_ENGLISH        "EMPTY INVENTORY"
LANG_CZECH        "PRAZDNY INVENTAR"

REFERENCE           FORCE_HEAL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Heal\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: Jedi have the ability to heal themselves after injury\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Leceni\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Jedi se vyleci po zraneni.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_JUMP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Jump\nDuration: Immediate\nArea Of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to make a tremendous vertical leap\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Skok\nTrvani: Bezprostredni\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi \nUcinek: Umozni Jedimu provest obrovsky skok do vysky.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_SPEED_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Speed\nDuration: 10 seconds\nArea of Effect: Jedi and surroundings\nEffect:  A Jedi speeds up and the world appears to slow down around them\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Rychlost\nTrvani: 10 sekund\nOblast ucinku: Jedi a jeho okoli\nUcinek: Jedi zrychli a diky tomu se zda, ze svet kolem nej se zpomalil.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_PUSH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Push\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Objects or Persons\nEffect: Allows Jedi to push objects away from themselves and defend from missile and Force Grip attacks\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Odstrceni\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Predmety nebo osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu odsouvat od sebe predmety, odrazet strely a branit se proti Sevreni.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_PULL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Pull\nDuration: Instantaneous effect\nArea Of Effect: Objects or Persons\nEffect: Allows Jedi to pull specific world objects to themselves\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Pritahnuti\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Predmety nebo osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu pritahnout k sobe urcite okolni objekty.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_MIND_TRICK_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Mind Trick\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Humanoids\nEffect: Allows Jedi to confuse and/or misdirect attention \n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Oklamani smyslu\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Humanoidi\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu zmast a/nebo odlakat pozornost.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_GRIP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Grip\nDuration: Instantaneous\nArea Of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to choke or constrict the organs of a living being\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Sevreni\nTrvani: Okamzite\nOblast ucinku: Pouze zive osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu skrtit nebo stisknout organy zivych bytosti.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_LIGHTNING_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Lightning\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to hurl a devastating electrical attack against enemies\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Blesk\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Pouze zive bytosti\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu vyslat devastujici elektricky vyboj proti nepratelum.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_SABER_DEFENSE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Lightsaber Defense\nDuration: Always on\nArea Of Effect: N/A\nEffect: Jedi can block damage with a lightsaber  \n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Obrana svetelnym mecem\nTrvani: Vzdy aktivni\nOblast ucinku: Jediho okoli\nUcinek: Jedi muze odrazit nebezpeci svetelnym mecem.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_SABER_OFFENSE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Lightsaber Offense\nDuration: Always on\nArea Of Effect: N/A\nEffect: As a Jedi gains combat experience, their lightsaber attack effectiveness increases\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Utok svetelnym mecem\nTrvani: Vzdy aktivni\nOblast ucinku: Jediho okoli\nUcinek: Jak Jedi ziskava bojove zkusenosti, zvysuje se ucinnost jeho utoku svetelnym mecem.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_SABER_THROW_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Lightsaber Throw\nDuration: Instant\nArea Of Effect: Player arc\nEffect:  A Jedi can throw a lightsaber and use it as a missile weapon\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Hod svetelnym mecem\nTrvani: Okamzity ucinek\nOblast ucinku: Vysec kolem hrace\nUcinek: Jedi muze hodit svetelny mec a pouzit ho jako vrhaci zbran.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_ABSORB_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Absorption\nDuration: 20 seconds\nArea Of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: Jedi can absorb dark Force power, Force Push and Force Pull directed at them\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Pohlceni\nTrvani: 20 sekund\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Jedi muze pohltit Temnou Silu, Odstrceni a Pritahnuti, ktere jsou na nej namireny.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_PROTECT_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Protection\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to decrease incoming damage from energy, physical, projectile, and explosive sources\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Ochrana\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu snizit utrpene poraneni z energetickych, fyzickych, strelnych a vybusnych zdroju.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_SENSE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Sense\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Objects or persons\nEffect: Allows Jedi to see people and objects that are invisible or behind solids\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Intuice\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Predmety nebo osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu videt lidi a predmety, ktere jsou neviditelne nebo za pevnymi plochami.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_DRAIN_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Drain\nDuration: Variable\nArea Of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to transfer the life essence of a person to themselves\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Odcerpani\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Pouze zive osoby\nUcinek: Umoznuje Jedimu prenaset do sebe trest zivota jinych osob.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_RAGE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Rage\nDuration: 10 seconds\nArea Of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: Affords Jedi protection against damage, an increase in speed, and an increase in damage potential, at the expense of health.  The Jedi needs some recovery time after a Rage ends\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Temna zurivost\nTrvani: 10 sekund\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Poskytuje Jedimu ochranu proti poraneni, vyssi rychlost a vyssi poskozujici potencial na ukor zdravi. Pote, co Temna zurivost skonci, potrebuje Jedi chvili na zotaveni.\n\n"

