REFERENCE           FAST_STYLE
LANG_ENGLISH        "Fast and efficient, but with limited range. Short, quick motions allow for multiple attacks but with minimum damage. This style can be chained indefinitely. It utilizes a defensive stance in which the Jedi holds his saber across his front in a ready position to fend off attacks or make quick jabs. Represented by a blue bar on the right side of the HUD."
LANG_CZECH        "Rychly styl\nRychly a efektivni, ale s omezenym dosahem. Kratke, rychle pohyby umoznuji vice utoku ale s minimalnim poranenim. Tento styl lze menit donekonecna. Vyuziva obranny postoj, ve kterem Jedi drzi svuj mec pred tvari v pohotovostni pozici, aby odrazil utoky nebo provedl rychle vypady. Je predstavovan modrym pruhem na prave strane HUDu."

REFERENCE           STRONG_STYLE
LANG_ENGLISH        "Uses powerful strikes to batter through defenses. This style incorporates great range and power, but often leaves the Jedi open for counter attack. It utilizes a powerful, aggressive stance in which the Jedi holds his saber high and back, ready to go into a heavy swing. Represented by a red bar  on the right side of the HUD."
LANG_CZECH        "Silovy styl\nVyuziva silne udery k probiti se skrz obranu. Tento styl zahrnuje velky dosah i silu, ale casto nechava Jediho nechraneneho pred protiutokem. Vyuziva silneho, agresivniho postoje, ve kterem drzi Jedi svuj mec vysoko a naprazeny dozadu, pripraveny prejit do silneho svihu. Je predstavovan cervenym pruhem na prave strane HUDu."

REFERENCE           CANT_SAVE_DEAD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Can't save game while dead!"
LANG_CZECH        "Po smrti nelze hru ulozit!"


//----------------------------------------------------------
//     Movie Duels NEW REFERENCES
//----------------------------------------------------------

REFERENCE	    BATTLEDROID_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Baktoid Armor E-5 Blaster Rifle\nThe E-5 blaster rifle was the standard issue blaster of the OOM and B1 battle droids and the elite BX-series droid commando during the Clone Wars. The E-5 blaster rifle was a powerful, light, but somewhat inaccurate weapon.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with moderate accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid, burst fire with low accuracy and expanded firing area\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack" 
LANG_CZECH        "Baktoid Armor E-5 blasterova puska\nE-5 blasterova puska byla standardni blasterova zbran OOM a B1 bitevnich droidu a elitnich droidich komand BX-serie behem Klonovych valek. E-5 blasterova puska byla silna, lehka, ale ponekud nepresna zbran.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel se stredni presnosti a velkou silou\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a vyssim palebnym dosahem\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    THEFIRSTORDER_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Sonn-Blas F-11D Blaster Rifle\nThe F-11D Blaster Rifle was the standard issue blaster of the First Order Stormtroopers during the First Order-Resistance Conflict. As the successor to the E-11, the F-11D came equipped with an adjustable J19 electroscope, magnatomic adhesion grip, and foregrip.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with moderate accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid, burst fire with low accuracy and expanded firing area\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Sonn-Blas F-11D blasterova puska\nF-11D blasterova puska byla standardni blasterova zbran Stormtrooperu Prvniho Radu behem konfliktu mezi Odbojem a Prvnim Radem. Jako nastupce E-11 byla F-11D vybavena nastavitelnym J19 elektrodalekohledem, magmatomickou prilnavou rukojeti a pazbou.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel se stredni presnosti a velkou silou\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a vyssim palebnym dosahem\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    CLONECARBINE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech DC-15S Blaster Carbine\nThe DC-15S Blaster Carbine was a standard issue weapon of the Clone Troopers of the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars. Smaller in scale than the DC-15A rifle, the DC-15S was considered easier to handle with a potentially higher rate of fire.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with moderate accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid, burst fire with low accuracy and expanded firing area\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech DC-15S blasterova karabina\nDC-15S blasterova karabina byla standardni blasterova zbran klonovych vojaku Velke armady Republiky behem Klonovych valek. Mela mensi rozmery nez puska DC-15A a byla povazovana za jednodussi na manipulaci s pripadnou vyssi rychlosti palby.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel se stredni presnosti a velkou silou\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a vyssim palebnym dosahem\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    REBELBLASTER_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech DH-17 Blaster Pistol\nThe DH-17 Blaster Pistol was a close-quarter automatic blaster pistol popularly used during the Galactic Civil War. Often favored by starship personnel in both the Rebel Alliance and Galactic Empire, the DH-17 was designed solely for close quarter combat, delivering lethal blasts with every shot, but suffered from poor accuracy at long range. Users of the blaster had to be careful, as prolonged use would drain its energy supply quickly, leaving the user defenseless.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with low accuracy and significant damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid, automatic fire with poor accuracy and significant damage.\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech DH-17 blasterova pistole\nDH-17 blasterova pistole byla automaticka zbran pro boj na blizke vzdalenosti, ktera byla popularni behem Galakticke obcanske valky. Casto vyuzivana posadkou lodi jak v Povstalecke Alianci, tak v Galaktickem Imperiu. DH-17 byla s kazdym vystrelem smrtelna, ale trpela spatnou presnosti na delsi vzdalenost. Uzivatele teto zbrane museli byt opatrni, protoze delsi pouzivani odcerpavalo zasoby energie a tim cinilo uzivatele bezbrannymi.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s malou presnosti a velkym poskozenim\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a velkym poskozenim\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    CLONERIFLE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech DC-15A Blaster Rifle\nThe DC-15A Blaster Rifle was a standard issue rifle of the Clone Troopers of the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars. Most prominently seen during the First Battle of Geonosis, the DC-15A was a long range rifle designed for open field combat, featuring a greater accuracy than the DC-15S, its carbine counterpart. \nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with good accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid fire with reduced accuracy and slightly expanded firing area\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech DC-15A blasterova puska\nDC-15A blasterova puska byla standardni blasterova zbran klonovych vojaku Velke armady Republiky behem Klonovych valek. Poprve byla videna behem Prvni bitvy o Geonosis. DC15-A byla puska v velkym dosahem vyrobena pro boj na bitevnim poli a poskytovala vetsi presnost nez DC-15S, jeji karabinovy protejsek.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel se dobrou presnosti a velkym poskozenim\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a vyssim palebnym dosahem\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    CLONECOMMANDO_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech DC-17m Interchangeable Weapon System\nThe DC-17m Interchangeable Weapon System was the standard issue weapon for the Clone Commandos of the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars. A versatile weapon, the DC-17m was a highly accurate weapon, with two other separate weapon configurations; sniper and anti-armor. In rifle mode, the weapon was incredibly accurate at most ranges, but was noticeably weak.\nPrimary Fire - Fast, single shot with perfect accuracy, yet weak damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid, burst fire with near-perfect accuracy\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech DC-17m vymenitelny zbranovy system\nDC-17m vymenitelny zbranovy system byla standardni blasterova zbran klonovych komand Velke armady Republiky behem Klonovych valek. DC-17m byla vsestranna a velmi presna zbran se dvema odlisnymi zbranovymi konfiguracemi; odstrelovac a anti-brneni. V odstrelovacim rezimu byla zbran neuveritelne presna ve vsech vzdalenostech, ale znatelne slabsi.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden rychly vystrel s perfektni presnosti, ale malym poskozenim\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva se skoro perfektni presnosti\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    REBELRIFLE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech A280 Blaster Rifle\nThe A280 Blaster Rifle was a weapon mostly used by the commandos of the Rebel Alliance during the Galactic Civil War. The A280 was well known for its armor piercing capabilities, with pinpoint accuracy and fair damage, but suffered from a slower rate of fire.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with pinpoint accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire - Slow automatic fire with pinpoint accuracy\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech A280 blasterova puska\nA280 blasterova puska byla zbran nejvice pouzivana komandy Povstalecke Aliance behem Galakticke obcanske valky. A280 byla dobre znama pro svoji schopnost prostrelit brneni s velkou presnosti a poskozenim, ale trpela na pomalejsi vystrely.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s perfektni presnosti a velkym poskozenim\nSekundardni utok - Pomala automaticka salva se skoro perfektni presnosti\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    Z6_ROTARY_CANNON_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Z6 Rotary Cannon\nThe Z6 Rotary Cannon was a powerful, high-caliber heavy blaster used by the Clone Troopers during the Clone Wars and later in the Galactic Civil War. Known for its devastating rate of fire and ability to mow down enemy infantry in seconds, the Z6 featured a rotating barrel that allowed for sustained fire without overheating. While the cannon’s sheer power and rapid fire made it effective against large groups of enemies, its weight and slow handling made it less suited for mobility.\nPrimary Fire - Continuous, high-rate of fire with moderate accuracy\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "Z6 rotacni kanon\nZ6 rotacni kanon byl vykonny tezky blaster velkeho kalibru, ktery pouzivali klonovi vojaci behem Klonovych valek a pozdeji behem Galakticke obcanske valky. Kanon Z6, znamy svou nicivou kadenci a schopnosti behem nekolika sekund zlikvidovat nepratelskou pechotu, byl vybaven rotujici hlavni, ktera umoznovala nepretrzitou palbu bez prehrati. Zatimco diky sve obrovske sile a rychle palbe bylo delo ucinne proti velkym skupinam nepratel, jeho hmotnost a pomala ovladatelnost ho cinily mene vhodnym pro mobilitu.\n\nPrimarni utok - Nepretrzita, vysoka kadence s prumernou presnosti\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    REY_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "LPA NN-14 Blaster Pistol\nThe NN-14 Blaster Pistol was a blaster pistol gifted to Rey by Han Solo during the First-Order Resistance Conflict. The NN-14 featured a compact grip, enlarged power core, and flash stabilizing muzzle. In combat, the NN-14 was favored for its near-pinpoint accuracy and great damage.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with great accuracy and damage\nSecondary Fire - Charged energy buildup for increased damage blast attack\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "LPA NN-14 blasterova pistole\nNN-14 blasterova pistole byla darem Rey od Hana Sola behem konfliktu Odboje s Prvnim Radem. NN-14 se skladala z kompaktni rukojete, zvetseneho napajeciho jadra a usti stabilizujici zablesk po vystrelu. V boji byla NN-14 oblibena pro svoji temer dokonalou presnost a poskozeni.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a silou\nSekundarni utok - Vytrysk nahromadene nabite energie s vyssi silou\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    JANGO_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "WESTAR-34 Blaster Pistol\nThe WESTAR-34 Blaster Pistol was the weapon of choice by bounty hunter Jango Fett prior to the Clone Wars. The WESTAR-34 fired powerful bolts that were very effective at close range, utilizing its dallorian construction to absorb more heat than a standard blaster.\nPrimary Fire - Single shot with great accuracy and low damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid fire with near-perfect accuracy, but low damage.\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "WESTAR-34 blasterova pistole\nWESTAR-34 blasterova pistole byla oblibenou zbrani lovce odmen Jango Fetta v obdobi pred Klonovymi valkami. WESTAR-34 strilela silne projektily, ktere byly velmi efektivni na blizkou vzdalenost. Zbran take vyuzivala dallorianskou konstrukci, ktera pohlcovala vice tepla, nez obvykly blaster.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a malym poskozenim\nSekundarni utok - Rychla strelba se skoro perfektni presnosti, ale s malym poskozenim\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    SBD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Super Battle Droid Weapon\nThe Player should never get this weapon \n If you have it then something is wrong"
LANG_CZECH        "Zbran Super bitevniho droida\nHrac by nikdy nemel obdrzet tuto zbran. Pokud ji mate, neco je spatne"

REFERENCE	    DUAL_PISTOL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "WESTAR-34 Dual Blaster Pistol\nThe WESTAR-34 Blaster Pistol was the weapon of choice by bounty hunter Jango Fett prior to the Clone Wars. The WESTAR-34 fired powerful bolts that were very effective at close range, utilizing its dallorian construction to absorb more heat than a standard blaster.\nPrimary Fire - Single shot with great accuracy and low damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid fire with near-perfect accuracy, but low damage.\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "WESTAR-34 blasterova pistole\nWESTAR-34 blasterova pistole byla oblibenou zbrani lovce odmen Jango Fetta v obdobi pred Klonovymi valkami. WESTAR-34 strilela silne projektily, ktere byly velmi efektivni na blizkou vzdalenost. Zbran take vyuzivala dallorianskou konstrukci, ktera pohlcovala vice tepla, nez obvykly blaster.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a malym poskozenim\nSekundarni utok - Rychla strelba se skoro perfektni presnosti, ale s malym poskozenim\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    BOBA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech EE-3 Carbine Rifle\nThe EE-3 Carbine Rifle was the weapon of choice by bounty hunter Boba Fett prior to and during the Galactic Civil War. Modeled after the E-11 Blaster Rifle, used by the infamous Stormtroopers of the Galactic Empire, the EE-3 featured a three shot burst that was highly effective at close range, but suffered at a longer range.\nPrimary Fire - Single shot with great accuracy and low damage\nSecondary Fire - Three shot burst fire with high accuracy, low damage, and minor fire delay.\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech EE-3 karabinova puska\nEE-3 karabinova puska byla oblibena zbran lovce odmen Boba Fetta pred a behem Galakticke obcanske valky. Byla vytvorena podle vzoru E-11 blasterove pusky, ktera byla pouzivana Stormtroopery Galaktickeho Imperia a umela strilet trojity vystrel, ktery byl vysoce efektivni na blizkou vzdalenost, ale trpel na delsi vzdalenosti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden vystrel s velkou presnosti a malym poskozenim\nSekundarni utok - Trojity vystrel s velkou presnosti, malym poskozenim a mensim spozdenim strelby.\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE	    CLONEPISTOL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech DC-17 Hand Pistol\nThe DC-17 Hand Pistol was the standard issue pistol to the Clone Troopers of the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars. An advanced firearm, the DC-17 was generally issued to the more elite and high ranking Clone Troopers such as ARC Troopers, Commanders, Captains, and Jet Troopers.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with great accuracy and damage\nSecondary Fire - Charged energy buildup for increased damage blast attack\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech DC-17 rucni pistole\nDC-17 rucni pistole byla standardni pistoli klonovych vojaku Velke Armady Republiky behem Klonovych valek. Byla to pokrocila strelna zbran, obvykle pouzivana elitnimi a vyse postavenymi klonovymi vojaky, jako ARC vojaky, komandery, kapitany a Tryskovymi vojaky.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a silou\nSekundarni utok - Vytrysk nahromadene nabite energie s vyssi silou\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           MELEE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Melee\nCommonly used as a last line of defence, melee combat is second skill of Jedi Knights. Many years of training in the art of unarmed combat ensure that Jedi is highly skilled without his lightsaber.\nPrimary Fire - Short range punch\nSecondary Fire - Kicks and Grab Katas"
LANG_CZECH        "Boj na blizko\nBezne pouzivana posledni linie obrany, boj na blizko je druha schopnost Jedie. Mnoho let treninku v umeni neozbrojeneho boje zajistuje, ze Jedi je vysoce zdatny i bez sveho svetelneho mece.\n\nPrimarni utok - Pestni udery na kratkou vzdalenost\nSekundarni utok - Kopy a specialni uchopeni"

REFERENCE           CLOAK_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Cloaking Shield\nThe cloaking shield renders the wearer invisible to others, allowing for stealthy movement.  However, due to the immense energy necessary to power the device, the cloak last for a short duration.  \n\nA direct hit from a DEMP 2 gun will temporarily disable the shield.  Additionally, a hit from the secondary fire of the DEMP 2 will permanently disable the shield."
LANG_CZECH        "Maskovaci stit\nMaskovaci stit skryje sveho nositele pred zraky ostatnich a umozni mu pohybovat se nepozorovane.  Nicmene, diky velke spotrebe energie, ktera pristroj napaji, maskovani trva pouze po kratkou dobu.\n\nPrimy zasah ze zbrane DEMP2 docasne zneaktivni stit.\nStrela ze sekundarniho utoku DEMP2 stit natrvalo vypne."  

REFERENCE	    BARRIER_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Gunners Personal Shield\nThis bubble energy field can be used by non saber wielders at any location, at which time it deploys a round shield that can block enemy fire.  The shield protects the body for a period of time.  The shield will disappear after expending its power supply or after enduring a certain amount of damage."
LANG_CZECH        "Osobni protizbranovy stit\nToto energeticke pole ve tvaru bubliny muze by pouzito temi, kteri nevlastni svetelny mec. Vytvori se kruhovy stit, ktery chrani pred nepratelskou palbou po urcity casovy interval. Stit zmizi po spotrebe sveho energetickeho zdroje nebo po vystaveni se urcite urovni poskozeni."

REFERENCE           JETPACK_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jetpack\nThe jetpack allows the wearer to fly for short durations, giving them a tactical advantage over others.  If the user does not fire the rockets, they will slowly lose altitude.\n\nThe jetpack is only usable in the Siege gametype.\n\n(Note:  To activate the jetpack, jump, then press 'use' while in the air.  Holding 'jump' will allow the user to gain altitude, while holding 'crouch' will decrease altitude.)"
LANG_CZECH        "Raketovy batoh\nRaketovy batoh umoznuje nositeli po kratkou dobu letat a tim mu ziskat taktickou vyhodu nad neprateli. Pokud uzivatel nezazehne trysky, tak postupne ztraci vysku.\n\n(Poznamka: K aktivaci raketoveho batohu vyskocte a pote stisknete klavesu 'pouzit', zatimco jste ve vzduchu.  Podrzeni 'skoku' umozni uzivateli ziskat vysku, zatimco podrzeni 'skrcit se' vysku snizi.)"

REFERENCE           WEAPON_BLASTER
NOTES		    "Edited name of original weapon"
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech E-11 Blaster Rifle"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech E-11 blasterova puska"

REFERENCE           BLASTER_RIFLE_DESC
NOTES		    "Edited description of original weapon"
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech E-11 Blaster Rifle \nThe primary weapon of the Imperial forces, the E-11 is a sturdy and deadly blaster rifle capable of inflicting great damage despite its small size.  The E-11's compact design makes it easy to carry and conceal.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with moderate accuracy and great damage\nSecondary Fire - Rapid, burst fire with low accuracy and expanded firing area\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech E-11 blasterova puska\nE-11 je zakladni zbrani vojaku Imperia. Je to stabilni a smrtici blasterova puska schopna zpusobit velke skody navzdory sve male velikosti. Kompaktni design E-11 umoznuje jeji snadne noseni a ukryti.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel se stredni presnosti a velkou silou\nSekundardni utok - Rychla salva s nizkou presnosti a vyssim palebnym dosahem\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

REFERENCE           WEAPON_THERMAL
NOTES		    "Edited name of original weapon"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Baradium-core Thermal Detonator"
LANG_CZECH        "Termalni detonator s baradiovym jadrem"

REFERENCE           THERMAL_DETONATOR_DESC
NOTES		    "Edited description of original weapon"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Baradium-core Thermal Detonator \nThe thermal detonator is a radius-damage grenade that creates an expanding particle field, vaporizing anything within its blast radius before it collapses after a small amount of time.\nPrimary Fire - Detonator explodes after about three seconds.  Press FIRE longer for longer throw\nSecondary Fire - Detonator explodes on impact.  Press ALT-FIRE longer for longer throw"
LANG_CZECH        "Termalni detonator s baradiovym jadrem\nTermalni detonator je granatem, ktery v urcitem okruhu kolem sebe uvolni vlnu termalni energie, ktera je schopna rozlozit veskerou hmotu.\n\nPrimarni utok - Granat exploduje po kratkem case. Pro delsi hod podrzte dele STRELBU\nSekundarni utok - Granat exploduje pri kontaktu. Pro delsi hod podrzte dele ALTERNATIVNI STRELBU"

