REFERENCE           TUSKEN_RIFLE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tusken Rifle \nThe standard projectile weapon used by the Tusken Raiders of Tatooine in ranged combat.   The long range weapon has impressive range and stopping power.\nPrimary Fire - Short range swing\nSecondary Fire - Single shot with slow fire rate\nAmmo Type - Power cell"
LANG_CZECH        "Tuskenska puska\nStandardni projektilova zbran pouzivana Tuskenskymi najezdniky na Tatooine pro boj na dalku. Zbran ma pozoruhodny dostrel a silu.\n\nPrimarny utok - Uder na blizko\nSekundarni utok - Jeden vystrel s pomalou rychlosti strelby\nDruh naboju - Energeticky clanek"

REFERENCE           NOGHRI_STICK_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Noghri Stick \nThe traditional melee weapon of the Tusken Raiders of Tatooine.   The weapon serves as a useful multipurpose tool and melee weapon.\nPrimary Fire - Overhead swing\nSecondary Fire - Uppercut swing\nAmmo Type - None"
LANG_CZECH        "Noghrijska hul\nTradicni soubojova zbran rasy Noghri. Zbran slouzi jako uzitecny nastroj pro mnoho veci a take jako zbran pro souboj na blizko.\n\nPrimarni utok - Svih pres hlavu\nSekundarni utok - Horni svih\nDruh naboju - Zadne"

REFERENCE           WEAPON_BLASTER_PISTOL
NOTES		    "Edited name of original weapon"
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech DL-44 Heavy Blaster Pistol"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech DL-44 tezka blasterova pistole"

REFERENCE           NEW_BLASTER_PISTOL_DESC
NOTES		    "Edited name of original weapon"
LANG_ENGLISH        "BlasTech DL-44 Heavy Blaster Pistol \nOne of the most common firearms in the galaxy, the BlasTech DL-44 Heavy Blaster Pistol is a hand-held energy weapon with a slow rate of fire and incredible accuracy.\nPrimary Fire - Slow, single shot with great accuracy and damage\nSecondary Fire - Charged energy buildup for increased damage blast attack\nAmmo Type - Blaster Pack"
LANG_CZECH        "BlasTech DL-44 tezka blasterova pistole\nTezka blasterova pistole DL-44 je jednou z nejbeznejsich zbrani v galaxii. Ma nizkou kadenci, ale je vysoce presna.\n\nPrimarni utok - Jeden pomaly vystrel s velkou presnosti a silou\nSekundarni utok - Vytrysk nahromadene nabite energie s vyssi silou\nDruh naboju - Sada naboju pro blastery"

