REFERENCE           WRIST_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mandalorian Armour Wrist Blaster\nThe Mandalorian Rocket Gauntlet is a wrist-mounted blaster based on the titular Mandalorian's gauntlets."
LANG_CZECH        "Mandaloriansky zapestni Blaster\nMandalorianska raketova rukavice je zapestni blaster vytvoreny na zaklade podoby Mandalorianovych rukavic."

REFERENCE	    GRAPPLE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Grapple Hook \nGrappling Hook is a device with multiple hooks attached to a rope; it is thrown, dropped, sunk, projected, or fastened directly by hand to where at least one hook may catch and hold. Generally, grappling hooks are used to temporarily secure one end of a rope."
LANG_CZECH        "Zachytny hak \nZachytny hak je zarizeni s nekolika haky pripojenymi k lanu; je hozen, upusten, potopen nebo pripevnen primo tam, kde se alespon jeden hak prichyti a drzi. Obvykle jsou zachytne haky pouzivany k docasnemu zabezpeceni konce lana."

