REFERENCE	    BLINDING
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Blinding:"

REFERENCE	    BLINDING2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Blinding"

REFERENCE	    FORCE_BLINDING_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Force Blinding\nDuration: Variable\nArea of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Force blinding was a telekinetic light side Force power. Upon use of this technique, a blinding flash of energy emanated from a user's hand, manifesting as a flash of light that overloaded a target's vision, causing temporary blindness.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLINDING_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - A powerful tool of the light side, a Jedi could obfuscate an opponent's sight, making it difficult for the adversary to spot and attack the Jedi or anyone else."

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLINDING_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - A powerful tool of the light side, a Jedi could obfuscate an opponent's sight, making it difficult for the adversary to spot and attack the Jedi or anyone else."

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLINDING_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - A powerful tool of the light side, a Jedi could obfuscate an opponent's sight, making it difficult for the adversary to spot and attack the Jedi or anyone else."

REFERENCE	    PROJECTION
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Projection:"
LANG_CZECH	   "Projekce:"

REFERENCE	    PROJECTION2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Projection"
LANG_CZECH	   "Projekce"

REFERENCE	    FORCE_PROJECTION_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Force Projection\nDuration: Variable\nArea of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: Force projection, also known as Similfuturus, was a Fallanassi Force technique recorded in the sacred Jedi texts and utilized by Jedi Master Luke Skywalker during the Battle of Crait.\n\n"
LANG_CZECH        "Projekce\nTrvani: Ruzne\nOblast ucinku: Pouze Jedi\nUcinek: Sila projekce, take znama jako Similfuturus, byla Fallanasska technika Sily zaznamenana v posvatnych textech radu Jedi a pouzita Mistrem Jedi Lukem Skywalkerem behem Bitvy o Crait.\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_PROJECTION_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - The technique allows a Jedi to create an illusory doppelganger of themselves that could be transmitted through the Force across vast distances."
LANG_CZECH        "Stupen 1 - Tato technika umoznuje Jedimu vytvorit iluzivniho dvojnika sebe sameho, ktery muze byt prenasen skrze Silu na velmi vzdalena mista."

REFERENCE           FORCE_PROJECTION_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - The technique allows a Jedi to create an illusory doppelganger of themselves that could be transmitted through the Force across vast distances."
LANG_CZECH        "Stupen 2 - Tato technika umoznuje Jedimu vytvorit iluzivniho dvojnika sebe sameho, ktery muze byt prenasen skrze Silu na velmi vzdalena mista."

REFERENCE           FORCE_PROJECTION_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - The technique allows a Jedi to create an illusory doppelganger of themselves that could be transmitted through the Force across vast distances."
LANG_CZECH        "Stupen 3 - Tato technika umoznuje Jedimu vytvorit iluzivniho dvojnika sebe sameho, ktery muze byt prenasen skrze Silu na velmi vzdalena mista."

